introduction: Welcome back everybody! This is the first Tipsrundan post-summer and we're happy to be back!

softValues.title: Everything I knew about reading was wrong
softValues.description: This title might sound clickbaty, but it's worth it. I think the ideas brought up, originally from Naval Ravikant, is brilliant. It's a new mindset that has helped me through the summer as I've tried to apply it. It feels a little bit like I finally get around to reading again!

random.title: Oh Shit, Git?
random.description: Did you just mess up? Don't know how to update? Then go here when in doubt, and save yourself!
